1573763,2026-03-31 06:13:18 -0700,2026-03-31 06:13:18 -0700,Mozilla VPN suggestion,"<p>Hi I just found VPN button in my browser turned it on and it works perfectly. i was very suprised because i am from russia and this vpn somehow can avoid DPI (deep packet inspection) that every isp has here in russia. My theory it is that mozilla vpn works because of IPv6, for now DPI can check and block only IPv4 connection.  suggestion - please add cryptocurrency as an additional payment method because we dont have visa or mastercard here since 2022. thank you </p>",firefox-1490;windows-1011;firefox;privacy-and-security_1;vpn;,firefox,privacy-and-security,en-US,"",forsberg09
